title: Working Football Manager Patch, Crash FIx, noSTEAM
description:

This is the first torrent I've upped, not sure what the rules are but needless to say it's not my fix, massive props to noSTEAM for that.  I'm up to mid-October so far.

Usual method applies, copy the patch into your save game folder, that contains the FM.exe file and run the patch. Play the game!!

AS it's my first upload, I'd appreciate if others could verify here that it is indeed kosher.

Cheers
